        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Congressional Foreign Entanglement Disclosure and Reduction Act</b></p> <p>This bill expands financial disclosure reporting provisions to require Members of Congress to include in their report any business ties the Member or his or her immediate family has with a foreign entity.</p>]]>
        </text>
